131
00:08:34,170 --> 00:08:36,069
kalau Tn. Genda mengalami tidur berjalan.

132
00:08:36,070 --> 00:08:39,469
Akan kujelaskan semuanya nanti.

133
00:08:39,470 --> 00:08:42,269
Dan bukankah kita akan

134
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:44,969
