145
00:11:56,185 --> 00:11:57,685
Atau, haruskah saya katakan...

146
00:12:01,085 --> 00:12:03,684
Tn. Morozumi.

147
00:12:03,685 --> 00:12:05,084
Ya.

148
00:12:05,085 --> 00:12:07,984
Gantungan kunci Kuda Kelinci Merah yang dibuat Tn. Genda

149
00:12:07,985 --> 00:12:09,984
